        {
            "id": 6422293,
            "title": "〈台股盤後〉輝積概念股衝高、聯電漲停 漲409點站上3萬7創新高",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>外界預期美伊有望達成停戰協議，美股昨 (15) 日多收紅，台股今 (16) 日台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 下午即將舉行法說會前，激勵台積電相關設備廠、IC 設計、輝達概念及光通訊股早盤開高走高，終場在台積電尾盤大單拉升下，大漲 409.88 點或漲 1.12%，收 37,132.02 點，日 K 連收 8 紅，成交量為 8,867.92 億元，較昨 (15) 日縮減近 1,000 億元。</p></section><p><template id=\"P:1\"></template></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>櫃買 (OTC) 則受惠多檔題材激勵，終場漲 1.7%，收 366.27 點表現優於上市指數。</p></section><section>\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>電子權值股今日漲跌互見，台積電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>) 因下午將舉行法說，股價在法說前已先起漲多日，今日開低震盪，尾盤在大單 5,352 張敲進下，小漲 5 元或 0.24% 收 2,085 元；聯發科 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2454:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2454\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2454-TW</a>) 漲半根停板、台達電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2308:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2308\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2308-TW</a>) 漲 3.3%；聯電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2303:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2303\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2303-TW</a>) 因受惠與光學材料 TFLN 領導廠 HyperLight 建立合作，未來有望打晉升光通訊技術，開盤早早亮燈漲停。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>鴻海 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2317:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2317\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2317-TW</a>) 小跌 0.24%、京元電子 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2449:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2449\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2449-TW</a>) 跌 2.58、 緯穎 (6669 -TW) 跌 0.54%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>面板股及 LED 股部分，富采 (3714 -TW) 因受惠整合友達 (矽光子)CPO 模組，盤中飆上漲停板，友達 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2409:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2409\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2409-TW</a>) 則漲 3.24。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>受惠輝達搶在周二 (14 日)，舉行「全球量子日」發表全球第一個量子 AI 開源模型，台廠輝達概念供應鏈包括南電 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8046:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8046\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8046-TW</a>) 閎康 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3587:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3587\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3587-TW</a>) 漲停、聯茂 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6213:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6213\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6213-TW</a>) 聯袂攻上漲停板，雙鴻 (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3324:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3324\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3324-TW</a>)、世芯 - KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3587:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3587\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3587-TW</a>) 漲 7-8%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>IC 設計族群則在盤中強勢翻揚，在買氣回籠下也帶動 AI 與高速傳輸概念熱潮，包括 神盾 (6462 -TW)、安格 (6684 -TW)、晶心科 (6533 -TW)、矽力 *-KY (<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:6415:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/6415\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">6415-TW</a>) 均攻上漲停。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>法人指出，指數短線多方氣勢強勁，預期戰爭對金融市場影響程度可望逐漸和緩降低影響，但利空對盤面仍有震盪影響，須提防漲多乖離個股，操作仍以選股不選市為主，短線則可持續觀察台積電法說會後，釋出的產業訊息走向。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p> </p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\">\n</section></main>",
            "link": "https://news.cnyes.com/news/id/6422293",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-16 14:23:26",
            "source": "cnyes",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
